      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used in the FEA ensemble (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1) must be under documented version control with traceable release notes, and all simulation scripts must be archived in a configuration-managed repository. Gradation 2 is required given medium model risk.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is a commercially validated finite element solver with documented QA procedures. The modeling team maintained version-controlled input decks in a Git repository with commit hashes recorded in the study report. Achieved Gradation 3 because independent code-level review was also performed by the FDA modeling team."
