    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors met or exceeded their required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) was accepted given that the COU is explicitly scoped to static compression-bending per ASTM F1717 and the single test condition is the standard protocol for this device type. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the intended regulatory decision at Medium assurance level.",
